data.description: This 1-story beauty in the community of Hidden Trails is move-in Ready! This lovely 3 bedroom 2 bath home features a light and bright open floor plan with a spacious living/dining combo that seamlessly feeds into the island kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar, pantry, stainless steel appliances and gas cooking. The primary suite includes a full bath with a large walk-in shower, double vanity, and roomy walk-in closet, and backyard view. The home also sports a home office, and well-sized secondary bedrooms, and backyard with a covered patio and privacy fence. There is something for everyone in this wonderful community, including a swimming pool, sports courts, clubhouse, trails, and fishing pier. Book your personal tour today!
